[ch]C[/ch] [ch]Am[/ch] [ch]C[/ch] [ch]Am[/ch]

versions.version_description: No capo, key of Em. Chords are slightly different than other versions (simplified for easy playing). This version is an easier key to sing the song in for those of us that are voice limited.

An ACTUAL transciption of the recording on Grace. For piano. Intro, bridge, outro, and everything. Sometimes Jeff sings an extension that isn't in the chord that he's playing. All chords are soley what he plays, not what he sings.
